2-tiered backup approach, meant for general use.

== backup: current

For small data that changes often, e.g. project work, config files

-- PERIOD
86400

-- RETAIN
daily	28
weekly	6
quarter	20

-- CRONTAB
daily	45  5  *  *  *
weekly	44  5  *  *  0
quarter	43  5  1 */3 *

== backup: archive

For large static data that doesn't change often, e.g. media

-- PERIOD
604800

-- RETAIN
weekly	4
monthly	12
yearly	5

-- CRONTAB
weekly	25  6  *  *  0
monthly	24  6  1  *  *
yearly	23  6  1  8  *

